  <div id="text-content_21983047-71c8-46d9-b662-f8f85c10fd45" class="text-block-content">
    <p>As an instructor, you may be able to limit the number of submission attempts allotted to students for an assignment. Limiting assignment attempts is only available for assignments with the Online submission type.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_assignments" data-step-uuid="44be86b2-463a-492f-bcc5-2f2c3c0157b5">
    <h2 id="open_assignments" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Assignments</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/354/327/original/d0cb82af-a6ef-42b6-be34-0531fc857d65.png" srcset="" alt="Open Assignments" height="271" width="169">
